content: I'm looking to get some tips on how to stay organized with my online shopping. I've been doing a lot of it lately, especially for new clothes. Speaking of which, I just got a few orders from ASOS last month - one was for a pair of jeans and some tops, and another was for a dress and some accessories. Do you have any advice on how to keep track of my online purchases and stay on top of my wardrobe updates?
